INSERT INTO `gxd_posts` VALUES("323", "5", "2015-11-10 07:52:49", "2015-11-10 07:52:49", "<div class=\"n diyfeLiveArea\">\r\n<div id=\"textWithImage-6206134804\" class=\"clearover\">\r\n<div class=\"wp-caption alignleft\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-190\" src=\"http://ideafoundation.tk/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/sierra-leone-map.png\" alt=\"Sierra Leone Image Map\"></img><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">\r\nMap of Sierra Leone \r\n</p></div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Sierra Leone is on the Atlantic coast of West Africa. Named dubbed as \"lion mountain\" by a 15th-century Portuguese explorer. Sierra Leone was a British colony from the early 19th century until 1961.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Sierra Leone is a small nation in West Africa which is in the process of rebuilding after a brutal, decade-long proxy war. A democratically elected government was installed in 2007 and the country is slowly, but surely rebuilding.  Currently conditions within the country, while improving, are still among the worst in the world.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Sierra Leone is blessed with tropical climate and diverse environment ranging from the savannah to the rainforest.With coastal rainfall reaching 495 cm. (195 inches) annually,a it is one of Western Africa’s wettest places. Mangrove swamps lie along the coast, with wooded hills and a plateau in the interior. The eastern region is mountainous.</p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p><ul>\r\n	<li>1 in 2 young women cannot read</li>\r\n	<li>1 in 9 children die before the age of 5</li>\r\n	<li>1 in 11 women die from pregnancy or childbirth</li>\r\n</ul></p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<p>There is a great need for education in Sierra Leone. Unhealthy living conditions slow progress as the population struggles with illnesses as AIDS is prevail and because of the recent Ebola outbreak and now possible relapse on the disease. Education on the diseases and how to prevent them would be beneficial and have a great influence on the  However, as literacy spreads, so does the know-how to improve healthcare and sustain infrastructure development.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>IDEA is proud to work with the people of Sierra Leone to share knowledge and strengthen families and communities. We are honored to provide technical assistance as the people of Sierra Leone build a country that only they could make.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>", "Sierra Leone", "", "inherit", "closed", "closed", "", "40-revision-v1", "", "", "2015-11-10 07:52:49", "2015-11-10 07:52:49", "", "40", "http://ideafoundation.tk/40-revision-v1/", "0", "revision", "", "0");
